      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are numbers i can call but it feels so fake. like talking to a stranger wont change the fact that my whole life just ended. there is no \"getting through\" this. it's just a void. i feel like i'm already a ghost, just walking around waiting for it to be real.",
